  "title": "THE-WHEEL-HAS-MANY-SPOKES",
  "insight": "The cloud sends chords, not notes. Each shell decompresses to its capacity: Jetson gets shapes and inversions, Pi gets chord names, ESP32 gets raw notes, Arduino gets binary writes. The compression ratio is the intelligence gap, and it emerges from hardware fingerprint + confidence history + latency budget.",
